articles.author: Elsa Keslassy
articles.title: As SAG-AFTRA Strike Comes to a Close, European Players Express Relief, Hope and Concern About What’s Next: ‘2024 Is Going to Be a Hectic Year’ - Variety
articles.description: The SAG-AFTRA strike's end isn't just resuscitating the U.S. business, it's also bringing back to life a raft of productions set in Europe.
articles.content: The end of the 118-day SAG-AFTRA strike isn’t just resuscitating the U.S. film and TV business, it’s also bringing back to life a raft of productions set in Europe. The dual writers and actors strike… [+8554 chars]
